AUDIO: 'The video opens on a kingdom in the clouds. We\'re not looking at a simple sky island. Cloud Whale City places an entire palace on the back of a whale gliding through fog. Notice how idogram 4.0 isn\'t just painting a fantasy animal. The image holds together as'

[00:12] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'architecture. As the camera drifts, we arrive at a table hovering on the edge of space. Null gravity dining plays with surreal physics, yet the restaurant layout still makes sense. Menus hang off to the side and there\'s a swirling plate'

[00:25] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'suspended by what looks like gravitational lensing. Idog 4.0 understands that even the wildest concept needs a menu layout, a reservation note, and typography that feels like fine dining. The model holds'

[00:37] [scene:talk]
