[07:59] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'how idio can miniaturaturize technology and arrange it in a museum layout with signage that looks curated. The museum of miniature disasters continues this miniature theme. Flood models, earthquake tables, tornado chambers,'

