AUDIO: 'avalanche slopes, blackout cities, and command boards occupy separate compartments. Each disaster scenario has its own label and environment, and the transitions between them feel natural. The model maintains coherence even when'

[08:25] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'combining multiple small worlds in one frame. After being swept away by worlds of imagination, we shift into pure information design. Idog 4.0 isn\'t just a dream machine. It\'s a diagram engine.'

