VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'whimsical mechanics with legible process flow. The Dream Engine breaks down a memory machine into labeled parts, a glass memory core, copper coil array, control dial, and memory capsule. Each component floats with call outs, and the'

[09:29] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'brass texture feels tangible. Exploded diagrams like this require spatial reasoning and label alignment. Capabilities Idog nails. With the foldable drone diagram and smartphone internals, the model moves into consumer'

[09:42] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'hardware. The mechanical camera and mechanical watch show similar control. Idoggram maintains perspective consistency across multiple exploded diagrams, something that makes or breaks technical illustration. Historical'

[09:55] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'infographics like the Nile trade system and the scriptorum demonstrate a different kind of structure. Here the model shows sensitivity to historical mood while still presenting clear information hierarchies. Modern engineering diagrams, electric vehicle'

[10:08] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'powertrain, renewable energy grid, anatomy of a quantum computer, how microchips are made, and the global smartphone supply chain rely on the same discipline. Battery packs connect to inverters, motors, and regenerative'

[10:21] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'braking systems. Solar panels feed into batteries and smart meters. Cryogenic stacks house cubits and control electronics. Wafer fabrication steps progress from photoresist to lithography, etching, and packaging. and'

[10:33] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'supply chains trace raw materials through assembly to recycling. Idog handles icons, arrows, step numbers, and callouts without misplacing them. This matters because AI image generation is'

[10:45] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'often used for visualizing emerging technologies, and clarity is non-negotiable. Process diagrams aren\'t limited to tech. How a court case moves explains filing, response, discovery, mediation, and trial. Journey of plastic'

[10:58] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'pollution traces plastic from street drains to oceans, microlastics, the food web and prevention strategies. Immune system defense shows barriers, inflammation, memory cells, and'

[11:10] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'antibbody responses, while the water cycle illustrates evaporation, condensation, precipitation, collection, and groundwater flow. In each case, the model keeps arrows pointing in the right direction and text aligned to the right'

[11:23] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'process, making complex topics approachable. Creative infographics like the high route and embroidered trail map stitched into fabric show how idiogram can stylize information while keeping it legible. The ridgeel line, base camp,'

[11:35] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'and pass markers all read clearly even though the medium is thread. Memory palace museum presents rooms such as childhood language, faces, skills, and the forgetting archive as a museum'

[11:47] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
