[12:25] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'in a single image. The desert brutalist villa cross-section shows thick walls storing cool air, solar roofs collecting energy, a shaded courtyard, and a suite tucked behind heavy concrete. Environmental strategy and spatial'

[12:38] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'design are communicated simultaneously. This is where the model\'s understanding of cutaways pays off. You can see how the climate strategy integrates with the architecture. On the other end of the spectrum is the skyline penthouse. The plan\'s clarity and the coherence of the'

[12:51] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'finishes show that idoggram can generate aspirational lifestyle layouts without losing spatial logic. Finally, the underground shelter plan pushes the cutaway approach underground. Idog handles subterranean structures with the'

[13:04] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'same clarity as surface level plans. Mystery and investigation call for visual storytelling. Case 47 is an evidence board connecting an alley photograph, a wristwatch, and a hotel room with red thread. Notes like follow'

[13:17] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
